  "en": {
    "title": "status - Global system diagnostics",
    "synopsis": "status",
    "description": "Display heap memory, SD storage, network connectivity, and partition status.",
    "details": "NAME\n  status - Diagnostic status.\n\nSYNOPSIS\n  status\n\nDESCRIPTION\n  Displays hardware and software diagnostics: OS version, uptime, heap, SD Card partitions, and network.\n\nSYSTEM ARCHITECTURE\n  Fetches statistics from '/api/status'. The ESP32 firmware intercepts this and queries internal ESP-IDF modules. See also web_api(7).\n\nEXIT CODES\n  0\n    Success.\n  1\n    Network query failed.\n\nCONFORMING TO\n  NucleoOS proprietary extension.\n\nAUTHOR\n  NucleoOS Core Devs.\n\nREPORTING BUGS\n  Report bugs to support@nucleoos.org.\n\nSEE ALSO\n  uptime(1), free(1), web_api(7)\n\nADVANCED EXAMPLES\n  status"
